WEBVTT

35:06.720 --> 35:09.240 line:80%
The terrain east of Chongzhou
is precipitous.

35:09.240 --> 35:09.990 line:80%
Easy to defend and hard to attack,

35:09.990 --> 35:11.450 line:80%
it is a natural barrier.

35:11.220 --> 35:13.940 line:80%
[Magistrate]

35:11.680 --> 35:13.310 line:80%
If the enemy holds their ground here,

35:13.310 --> 35:14.430 line:80%
our army will struggle to cross.

35:14.010 --> 35:18.740 line:80%
[The world is benevolent]

35:15.160 --> 35:15.910 line:80%
